{{Top|leg}}
'''Old Janx Spirit''' was a strong, distilled [[Alcohol/Legends|liquor]]. It&mdash;along with [[Sullustan gin]] and [[Spicebrew/Legends|spicebrew]]&mdash;could be used to make the cocktail [[Sonic Servodriver]].<ref name="ms2">''[[MedStar II: Jedi Healer]]''</ref>

[[Juno Eclipse/Legends|Juno Eclipse]] had a bottle in her safe aboard the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|frigate]] [[Salvation (flagship)|''Salvation'']], which she planned to open when [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] was dead.<ref name="FU2">[[Star Wars: The Force Unleashed II (novelization)|''Star Wars: The Force Unleashed II'' novelization]]</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
[[W:c:hitchhikers:Janx Spirit|"Old Janx Spirit"]] is also the name of an alcoholic beverage mentioned in the radio play and novel versions of [[W:c:hitchhikers:The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy|''The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy'']].<ref name="TERC">''[[The Essential Reader's Companion]]''</ref>

